name: Tyger Tyger Collectors Edition
description:
TYGER TYGER
poem by William Blake
illustrations by Mert Yavasca / BukeNFT
Tyger Tyger series - consists of 6 pages - was put on sale in October 2021 on the hicetnunc. 
20 editions was minted from each 6 pages. All editions completely sold out.
This PDF booklet is dedicated to collectors who bought all 6 pages in the series.
